  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Electrical/ Service Engineer",
  "description": "<p>Our esteemed client in the <strong>Electrical Engineering/ Manufacturing industry</strong> is seeking a <strong>Service Engineer </strong>to join their dynamic team:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Employment Type: </strong>Permanent</li>\n  <li><strong>Position:</strong> Service Engineer (Electrical)</li>\n  <li><strong>Location:</strong> East</li>\n  <li><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Monday to Friday, 8am to 5.30pm</li>\n  <li><strong>Salary Package:</strong> Basic + Bonus (more than 1 month)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Responsible for the installation, commissioning, maintenance, and testing of high- and medium-voltage equipment.</li>\n  <li>Prepare and submit service reports after fieldwork.</li>\n  <li>Provide technical support and product knowledge to clients.</li>\n  <li>Maintain equipment records and update product database.</li>\n  <li>Stay updated on technical and industry developments.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum a Degree in Electrical &amp; Electronic Engineering with at least 1 year of field experience in high/medium voltage systems.</li>\n  <li>Candidates with Class 3 driving license would be an advantage.</li>\n  <li>Able to travel across the region for job assignments as and when required.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Ready to apply? Here’s how:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Click the APPLY button, or</li>\n  <li>Email your resume (in MS Word or PDF format) to <a href=\"mailto:adelin@intuitrecruitment.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>adelin@intuitrecruitment.com</strong>.</a> Include the job title in your email subject line for prompt processing.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em><strong>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>By submitting your application, you consent to the collection and use of your personal data under Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Adelin Chong | EA Personnel Reg No.: R1875641</p>\n<p>Intuit Recruitment Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 25C2793</p>",
